Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: NY newspaper strike ends
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bv74
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Nov 1978
New York newspapers back on the streets after three-month strike. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.